lead_paragraph: A fluent Liverpool moved second in the Premier League with a 2-1 win over West Bromwich Albion at Anfield on Saturday but will rue missing the prize of top spot a larger margin of victory would have secured.

headline.print_headline: Fluent Liverpool Beat West Brom but Miss Out on Top Spot
